        "name": "Extract Device ID",
        "func": "// Save the original sensor data so we don't lose it\nmsg.originalData = msg.payload; \n\n// Format the query to look for this specific device_id\nmsg.payload = [{ \"device_id\": msg.payload.device_id }]; \n\nreturn msg;",
